snippet.title: Mega Man Battle Network Legacy Collection - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Coming April 14th to PlayStation, Switch, and PC, Mega Man Battle Network Legacy Collection collects ten classic games from the Battle Network series. The release includes all 499 Patch Cards from the series!
